			'<p>Please submit your application with your CV / resume attached at:\n<a href="https://apply.workable.com/talkspace/j/FF6B66431C/">https://apply.workable.com/talkspace/j/FF6B66431C/</a></p>\n<p>*Must be willing to complete a 15-20 hour take-home assignment</p>\n',
